.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-OPEN-BATCH" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-open-batch \- open multiple channels in one command
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-open-batch
.I peer_id:sat
.RI [ peer_id:sat " ...]"
.SH DESCRIPTION
Opens one channel per
.IR peer_id:sat
argument by calling
.B lightning-cli fundchannel
for each pair in sequence.
Returns an array of results, one per argument.
Returns an error object if no arguments are provided.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{peer_id, channel_id, ok},...]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-open (1),
.BR lightning-channel-open-dual (1)
